{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Why do so many people reach success and then fail?"},{"time":5000,"text":"One of the big reasons is, we think success is a one-way street."},{"time":9000,"text":"So we do everything that leads up to success,"},{"time":11000,"text":"but then we get there. We figure we've made it,"},{"time":13000,"text":"we sit back in our comfort zone,"},{"time":15000,"text":"and we actually stop doing everything that made us successful."},{"time":18000,"text":"And it doesn't take long to go downhill."},{"time":20000,"text":"And I can tell you this happens,"},{"time":22000,"text":"because it happened to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25000,"text":"Reaching success, I worked hard, I pushed myself."},{"time":28000,"text":"But then I stopped, because I figured, \"Oh, you know, I made it."},{"time":31000,"text":"I can just sit back and relax.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"Reaching success, I always tried to improve and do good work."},{"time":37000,"text":"But then I stopped because I figured, \"Hey, I'm good enough."},{"time":40000,"text":"I don't need to improve any more.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":42000,"text":"Reaching success, I was pretty good at coming up with good ideas."},{"time":46000,"text":"Because I did all these simple things that led to ideas."},{"time":49000,"text":"But then I stopped, because I figured I was this hot-shot guy"},{"time":52000,"text":"and I shouldn't have to work at ideas, they should just come like magic."},{"time":55000,"text":"And the only thing that came was creative block."},{"time":57000,"text":"I couldn't come up with any ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"Reaching success, I always focused on clients and projects,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and ignored the money. Then all this money started pouring in."},{"time":66000,"text":"And I got distracted by it."},{"time":68000,"text":"And suddenly I was on the phone to my stockbroker and my real estate agent,"},{"time":71000,"text":"when I should have been talking to my clients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"And reaching success, I always did what I loved."},{"time":77000,"text":"But then I got into stuff that I didn't love,"},{"time":79000,"text":"like management. I am the world's worst manager,"},{"time":82000,"text":"but I figured I should be doing it, because I was, after all,"},{"time":84000,"text":"the president of the company."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"Well, soon a black cloud formed over my head"},{"time":89000,"text":"and here I was, outwardly very successful,"},{"time":91000,"text":"but inwardly very depressed."},{"time":93000,"text":"But I'm a guy; I knew how to fix it."},{"time":97000,"text":"I bought a fast car."},{"time":99000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":102000,"text":"It didn't help."},{"time":104000,"text":"I was faster but just as depressed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"So I went to my doctor. I said, \"Doc,"},{"time":109000,"text":"I can buy anything I want. But I'm not happy. I'm depressed."},{"time":113000,"text":"It's true what they say, and I didn't believe it until it happened to me."},{"time":116000,"text":"But money can't buy happiness.\""},{"time":119000,"text":"He said, \"No. But it can buy Prozac.\""},{"time":122000,"text":"And he put me on anti-depressants."},{"time":124000,"text":"And yeah, the black cloud faded a little bit, but so did all the work,"},{"time":128000,"text":"because I was just floating along. I couldn't care less if clients ever called."},{"time":132000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":135000,"text":"And clients didn't call."},{"time":137000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":138000,"text":"Because they could see I was no longer serving them,"},{"time":140000,"text":"I was only serving myself."},{"time":142000,"text":"So they took their money and their projects to others who would serve them better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"Well, it didn't take long for business to drop like a rock."},{"time":149000,"text":"My partner and I, Thom, we had to let all our employees go."},{"time":153000,"text":"It was down to just the two of us, and we were about to go under."},{"time":155000,"text":"And that was great."},{"time":157000,"text":"Because with no employees, there was nobody for me to manage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"So I went back to doing the projects I loved."},{"time":164000,"text":"I had fun again, I worked harder and, to cut a long story short,"},{"time":168000,"text":"did all the things that took me back up to success."},{"time":171000,"text":"But it wasn't a quick trip."},{"time":173000,"text":"It took seven years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"But in the end, business grew bigger than ever."},{"time":178000,"text":"And when I went back to following these eight principles,"},{"time":181000,"text":"the black cloud over my head disappeared altogether."},{"time":184000,"text":"And I woke up one day and I said,"},{"time":186000,"text":"\"I don't need Prozac anymore.\""},{"time":188000,"text":"And I threw it away and haven't needed it since."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190000,"text":"I learned that success isn't a one-way street."},{"time":193000,"text":"It doesn't look like this; it really looks more like this."},{"time":196000,"text":"It's a continuous journey."},{"time":198000,"text":"And if we want to avoid \"success-to-failure-syndrome,\""},{"time":201000,"text":"we just keep following these eight principles,"},{"time":203000,"text":"because that is not only how we achieve success,"},{"time":206000,"text":"it's how we sustain it."},{"time":208000,"text":"So here is to your continued success."},{"time":210000,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":212000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}